sourcesContent: import React, {Fragment} from 'react'; import { Button } from '../buttons/Button.jsx'; import image from './svg-2.svg'; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, TextWrapper, Subheading, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, Column2, ImgWrap, Img } from './InfoElements'; const Info = ({id, imgStart, topLine, headline, description, buttonLabel, img, alt}) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headline} With Maya you can gift a star to a loved one. {description} Our upcoming cryptocurrency allows for anyone to participate in the world's first decentralized star database. ) } export default Info;
